Subject: Dictated Narrative Subject File Index Source

Description: Preserved source for defining an index of narrative subject matters to files of interest.

& [DictatedNarrativeSubjectFileIndexSource] is preserved user direction
  + [source_time] is 2026-06-24
  + [source_type] is dictated refinement
  + [source_scope] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop narrative layer and attention indexing
  + [raw_direction] is "that suggests we need an index of the subject matters in the narrative layer detailing the files of interest in respect to each of the narrated subjects. I don't think that's part of the overall system yet?"
  + [interpreted_need] is define a narrative-subject index that maps narrated subject matters to the SOP files of interest for re-entry, search, review, and deeper inquiry
  + [inside] is narrative subject keys, files of interest, relation reasons, depth hints, authority boundaries, unresolved subjects, and table-backed lookup
  + [boundary] is SOP-only specification, local Pinky .sop authority, source preservation, no runtime mutation, and no exhaustive coverage claim
  + [outside] is hidden model state, automatic file authority, complete repository coverage, worker mutation, and unrelated dirty files

  = must: preserve this direction separately from canonical contracts
  = must: keep the index as search and re-entry guidance rather than proof of meaning
  = must: distinguish narrative subject indexing from semantic hash lookup and surface periphery lookup
